\nand validate the experimental velocity profiles for these different impact\nconfigurations. The novel ability of the employed experimental setup to measure\nfull-field free surface velocities with high spatial resolutions in shock\ncompression experiments is demonstrated for the first time in this work.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 22 Oct 2022 23:02:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-08"}
